OL,3,CFM pays tribute to former Senedd
OL,4,CMember who has died
OL,6,FThe First Minister has paid tribute to
OL,7,Fformer Senedd Member Caroline Jones
OL,8,Fwho has died at the age of 71.
OL,10,FCaroline Jones was a UKIP Assembly
OL,11,FMember from May 2016 and April 2021
OL,12,Ffor South Wales West and stood in last
OL,13,Fweek's election as an Independent
OL,14,Fcandidate.
OL,16,FIn a statement, First Minister Rhun ap
OL,17,FIorwerth said: "I am saddened to hear
OL,18,Fabout the sudden passing Caroline
OL,19,FJones. Caroline was always kind and
OL,20,Fvery generous to me.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
