OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778782268
OL,3,CFM pays tribute to former Senedd
OL,4,CMember who has died
OL,6,F"My condolences are with her family
OL,7,Fand friends."
OL,9,FOn the evening of May 12, her husband
OL,10,FAlun Williams announced on Facebook
OL,11,Fthat she was in palliative care after
OL,12,Fa sudden diagnosis of sepsis.
OL,14,FHe wrote: "It is with heavy hearts
OL,15,Fthat I must share that Caroline Jones
OL,16,Fis currently receiving palliative care
OL,17,Ffollowing a diagnosis of severe sepsis.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
