OL,3,CFM pays tribute to former Senedd
OL,4,CMember who has died
OL,6,FMs Jones joined Reform UK in 2023 and
OL,7,Fstood as the party's candidate for
OL,8,FBridgend in the 2024 General Election.
OL,9,FShe quit the party in April this year
OL,10,Fand instead ran as stood as an
OL,11,FIndependent for Pen-y-bont Bro
OL,12,FMorgannwg.
OL,14,FReform UK Senedd Member for Blaenau
OL,15,FGwent Caerffili Rhymni, Llyr Powell,
OL,16,Fsaid: "I have known Caroline Jones for
OL,17,Fover 15 years and I am shocked and
OL,18,Fsaddened by today's news.
OL,20,F"My thoughts and prayers are with her
OL,21,Floved ones at this difficult time."
